icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Operating Hours &amp; Seasons</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\" width=\"100%\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5541988\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"on the left, rustic stone observation building. to the right, a complex landscape of colorful pinnacles and peaks within Grand Canyon\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/IMG_8460.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Lookout Studio Panorama\"/>\n<figcaption>Lookout Studio in Grand Canyon Village on the South Rim of the park. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6070914\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6070914\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1959245\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1959245\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>South Rim: Open Year-round</h2>\n<p style=\"Color : darkolivegreen\"><span style=\"line-height : 1.42857\"><font color=\"#464646\">The </font></span><strong><span style=\"line-height : 1.42857\"><font color=\"darkolivegreen\">South Rim</font></span></strong><span style=\"line-height : 1.42857\"><font color=\"#464646\"> of the park is open 24 hours a day, 365 days a year. The South Rim includes Grand Canyon Village and Desert View. Most services are available year-round.</font></span> <strong><span style=\"line-height : 1.42857\"><font color=\"#464646\">Reservations are strongly recommended during spring, summer and fall</font></span></strong><span style=\"line-height : 1.42857\"><font color=\"#464646\">. Some facilities close during winter months.</font></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"Font-Size : 13pt\"><font color=\"#666666\">Follow links to obtain operating hours and information for:</font></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6714073,/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Entrance Fee Costs and Pass Options</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/lodging.htm\"><span id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878476,lodging.htm,11006|\">South Rim: Lodging</span></a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/cg-sr.htm\"><span id=\"CP___PAGEID=1954247,cg-sr.htm,11006|\"><strong>South Rim: Campgrounds</strong></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"CP___PAGEID=1954247,cg-sr.htm,11006|\"><strong><span id=\"CP___PAGEID=1870415,visitorcenters.htm#CP_JUMP_2129152,11006|\"><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/visitorcenters.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1870415,/grca/planyourvisit/visitorcenters.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">South Rim: Visitor Centers and Museums </a></span></strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/shuttle-buses.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1914943,shuttle-buses.htm,11006|\">South Rim: Free Shuttle Bus Service</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878498,/grca/planyourvisit/restaurants.htm,11006|\"><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/restaurants.htm\">South Rim: Restaurants and Groceries</a> </strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/goodsandservices.htm\"><span id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878833,goodsandservices.htm,11006|\"><strong>South Rim: Goods and Services</strong></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/things2do.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1829735,things2do.htm,11006|\">South Rim: Things to Do</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/sr-programs.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=7551740,/grca/planyourvisit/sr-programs.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">South Rim Village: Ranger Programs and Special Events</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">South Rim, Desert View: Open Year-round</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/desert-view.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=837948,desert-view.htm,11006|\">Desert View - Visitor Services</a> </strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/desert-view-cultural-demonstration-program.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=7266783,desert-view-cultural-demonstration-program.htm,11006|\">Desert View - Cultural Demonstrations</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Phantom Ranch</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth-03.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2616090,grand-canyon-in-depth-03.htm,14075|\">Phantom Ranch Information</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<em style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; background-color: var(--bs-body-bg); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Througout the park, Reservations for Lodging and Camping are strongly recommended.</em>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_839275\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_839275\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr align=\"left\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"1\" title=\"\"/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2140043\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<a id=\"northrim\"></a><a id=\"CP_JUMP_2140043\"></a><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2140043\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">North Rim</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/grca/northrimstatus.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=8060425,northrimstatus.htm,10957|\">North Rim - Current Status and Closures</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5920786\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5920786\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">All Visitors MUST Have an Entrance Pass</span></h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6714073,/grca/planyourvisit/fees.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Learn about entrance fee costs and annual passes </a> &gt;</strong></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6709480\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6709480\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr>\n</hr></div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6691962\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6691962\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p><em><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/grand-canyon-national-park-public-health-update.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6397341,/grca/planyourvisit/grand-canyon-national-park-public-health-update.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Visit this webpage</a><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong> (updated daily) for the current list of what is open and closed, and the hours of operation. </strong></span></em></p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x2x1\" width=\"100%\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"/commonspot/images/clear.gif\" style=\"display:block;\" width=\"1\"/></td></tr><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x3x1\" width=\"100%\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"/commonspot/images/clear.gif\" style=\"display:block;\" width=\"1\"/></td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm